{"word":"Ethiopia","slug":"ethiopia","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ethiopia</b> <a href=\"#/H3568\">H3568</a> <br/> A region in Africa, inhabited by the descendants of Ham.<br/> The inhabitants of, black<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=13&verse=23'>Jer 13:23</a><br/> Within the Babylonian empire<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=1'>Est 1:1</a><br/> Rivers of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=6'>Gen 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=18&verse=1'>Isa 18:1</a><br/> Bordered Egypt on the south<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=29&verse=10'>Eze 29:10</a><br/> Was called the Land of Cush<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=6'>Gen 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=9'>1Ch 1:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=11&verse=11'>Isa 11:11</a><br/> Warriors of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=9'>Jer 46:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=12&verse=3'>2Ch 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=38&verse=5'>Eze 38:5</a><br/> Defeated by Asa<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=14&verse=15'>2Ch 14:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=16&verse=8'>2Ch 16:8</a><br/> Invaded Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=19&verse=9'>2Ki 19:9</a><br/> Merchandise of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=45&verse=14'>Isa 45:14</a><br/> Moses marries a woman of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=1'>Num 12:1</a><br/> Ebel-melech, at the court of Babylon, native of; kindly treats Jeremiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=13'>J